OL,6,FA woman was left "bereft" after losing
OL,7,Fnearly #70,000 of lifesavings to
OL,8,Ffraudsters who made her believe her
OL,9,Fbank account was being raided, a court
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FThe woman was duped after clicking on
OL,13,Fa bogus Post Office link in a text
OL,14,Fmessage in May 2022 telling her she
OL,15,Fneeded to pay a #1.20 fee for a postal
OL,16,Fdelivery.
