OL,3,CWoman left 'bereft' after losing
OL,4,C#70,000 in text message scam
OL,6,FAfter receiving a phone call warning
OL,7,Fher that an attempt had been made to
OL,8,Ftake #1,200 from her bank account, she
OL,9,Ffollowed an instruction to transfer
OL,10,Fnearly #20,000 into what she thought
OL,11,Fwas a safe account, Hull Crown Court
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FProsecutor Samantha Laws said: "She
OL,15,Falso transferred other large sums of
OL,16,Fmoney."
OL,18,FThe woman's total losses amounted to
OL,19,F#69,566.
