OL,3,CWoman left 'bereft' after losing
OL,4,C#70,000 in text message scam
OL,6,FIn a statement, the woman said the
OL,7,Fmental toll had been "horrific".
OL,9,F"I could not believe how stupid I have
OL,10,Fbeen," she said. "It was a constant
OL,11,Fnoise in the back of my head. I really
OL,12,Fstruggled. There has not been a single
OL,13,Fday in the last two years where I have
OL,14,Fnot thought about it. It was my nest
OL,15,Fegg that I had built for the future.
OL,17,F"I felt bereft. It had really knocked
OL,18,Fmy confidence in myself. All my
OL,19,Fsavings that I had worked hard for had
OL,20,Fbeen taken. I did not know what to do."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
