OL,3,CWoman left 'bereft' after losing
OL,4,C#70,000 in text message scam
OL,6,FAnother woman also fell victim to the
OL,7,Fscam, the court heard.
OL,9,FDan Gheorghe, 23, of Edgecumbe Street,
OL,10,Fwest Hull, admitted two offences of
OL,11,Ftransferring criminal property.
OL,13,FJudge Mark Bury said he was involved
OL,14,Fin "money laundering" by using bank
OL,15,Faccounts to falsely obtain people's
OL,16,Fmoney, but he did not substantially
OL,17,Fbenefit.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
