OL,3,CWoman left 'bereft' after losing
OL,4,C#70,000 in text message scam
OL,6,F"Other people were operating a scam
OL,7,Fdesigned to trick money from law-
OL,8,Fabiding people who have saved it up,"
OL,9,FJudge Bury said.
OL,11,F"That money ended up in bank accounts
OL,12,Fwhich you opened. Your basis of plea,
OL,13,Faccepted by the prosecution, was to
OL,14,Fthe effect that this was your total
OL,15,Finvolvement in this.
OL,17,F"You didn't make either any or, at
OL,18,Fleast, very much out of it. Had you
OL,19,Fbeen involved in the enterprise that
OL,20,Fcaused so much heartache, you would
OL,21,Fhave been going to prison."
